  "description": {
   "en": "A person who lives in clothes. The sound of a sewing machine echoing in a nostalgic townscape. Inheriting the aspirations of his grandmother, he continues to make clothes that are unique to him and that can be worn for the rest of his life. Ichie, the owner of such a South Dressmaking shop, and Fujii, a department store planning department who loves her clothes. It is a gentle and gentle story that depicts the thoughts of the two people involved while maintaining a delicate sense of distance and the people involved in clothing.\n\nsource: https://www.mangaupdates.com/series/9t1gyq7/tsukuroi-tatsu-hito"
